Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:49.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:54.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:24.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:30.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:35.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:44.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:50.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:56.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:01.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally found a tree to call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is born into this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right, Saul.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... I'll try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Do it! Do it, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do it, Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a ghost town here!\NEveryone's already there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I know our duty is to ensure the\Ntrain leaves safely, but I can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we're late for the party\Nheld for the entire town...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I can't... run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go to Paulie-san's\Nparty no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's Paulie-san's?! I didn't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town is still in the\Nprocess of being restored,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet Straw Hat is holding\Na big party at Galley-La!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wedding party!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I can't\Njust sit around like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're important to them,\Nsince we witnessed that precious moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Am I wrong?\N--You're not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may even end up having to deliver\Na congratulatory speech! Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us go, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! Entrant #9985, Sogeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing about the pride of\Nthe man hidden behind the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I was born on the island of snipers! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ I never miss my mark! Lulu lala lu! ♪\N--Yow, yow, yow, yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is far from over!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Let's all party!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shanks Makes a Move!\NThe Linchpin to the Reckless Era"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five Elder Stars! Five Elder Stars!\NSomething terrible has happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fleet we sent out to the New World\Nthe other day has been defeated...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Red-Haired Shanks and Edward Newgate,\Naka Whitebeard, two of the Four Emperors,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are finally about to make direct contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Hair wants to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Let him come aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat better have brought good booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:57.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that the fleet has been defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Red Hair and Whitebeard will be in contact?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! We don't know\Nwhat will happen next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by on maximum alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destination straight ahead! Furl the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Red Hair is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Hair is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greenhorns oughta stay back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...unless you wanna get knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.79,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knocked out?! What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go to the back and stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I guess it's already too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, guys! Say something! Hey!\N--Don't make a fuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've just been knocked\Nunconscious, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who lack the mettle can't even\Nstay conscious in front of that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's got an incredibly strong Haki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me... for the bit of intimidation\NI gave off, since I'm on an enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I see your face,\Nthe scar that guy gave me throbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:50.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alcohol"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some healing spirits with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to fight.\NThere's something I want to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Says the man who shows up\Nthrowing his Haki around?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Red Hair! What'd you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're Marco of the first division, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you join my gang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, what should we...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.07,0:10:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, looks like there won't\Nbe a battle. Leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This booze is from the West Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the cheap stuff, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having traveled around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find nothing's better than the booze\Nmade from the water I grew up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's booze from my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger, Garp, Sengoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't that many people\Nleft who know about that era.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 22 years. That's just natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have worked your way up the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just a young apprentice\Non Gol D. Roger's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we were fighting Roger's\Ngang all the time back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you and I got acquainted in an unusual way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we've found you!\NYou can't escape anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna dye that beard of yours blood red!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, my nose isn't blood red!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has that funny Red-nose who was\Nwith you kicked the bucket yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Buggy? That brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We parted in Loguetown
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the day our captain was executed,\Nand I haven't seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:12:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to be your subordinate, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he's still a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, the time seemed to flash by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many pass down stories about the days when\Nyou and Hawk-Eye used to duel like legends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but those days seem like yesterday to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone of your caliber lost\None of his arms in the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What enemy did you give your left arm to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't gonna take you anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'm gonna gather a crew\Nevery bit as good as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna find the greatest\Ntreasure in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna be King of\Nthe Pirates! I'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it... on a new era.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, as long as you have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've experienced many battles\Nand received many scars,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the scar that throbs right now is this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't a wound from an adventure\Nor one received from Hawk-Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who gave me this scar\Nwas one of your men...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't let my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:14:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get what I want to say, Whitebeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was quietly waiting for the right moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't become a\Ncommander or make his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept his true self hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stood in the shadow of the\Ngreat pirate Whitebeard all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, he's gained power\Nand started to make his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he'll aim for the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his own will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he'll eventually come\Nto take even your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?\NThat's what you came to talk about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he's young, you made him\Nyour second division commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that fame and trust\Nmake the matter complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too soon to have those two fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from Blackbeard Teach!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I want to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man's laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you'd talk to me like that...\NThat snot-nosed brat sure did grow a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His crime was killing one of his crewmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the worst sin you\Ncan commit on a pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He broke the golden rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I let them board my ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.59,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are all my sons,\Nno matter how foolish they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can my killed son's soul go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my responsibility to show that idiot Teach
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you can't make your way in the\Nworld if you lack a moral code, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 100 years too soon to tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will be able to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this reckless era!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Red Hair, that bastard!\NWhat's he doing to the old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. He's not the type\Nto pull a stupid stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever discussion they\Nhad seems to have fallen apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look above.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clouds have... No, the sky has been split!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.35,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I got today's newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's talking about Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So it's finally in the news?!\NHey, what's it saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an article that'll determine our fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well...\N--W-Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...talking about us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! We have no choice\Nbut to leave this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?! It's not talking about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--Not at all?! Is that possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I thought we had to\Nlive life on the run! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal, when the Franky\NFamily went on such a rampage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe your grandpa spun\Nthe information by saying
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they were regular people\Nwho got dragged into the incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't think he'd even think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he would, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it's Aokiji who did it.\NHe's hard to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, that's good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pirates, but they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they had to live life on the run\Nfrom here on out, I'd feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, they wrote terrible things about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to this, we declared\Nwar on the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even burning down the island\Nwas our doing, it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our bounties will go up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you think I'll get a bounty, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm the one who's gonna be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A superstar appears."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys happy about it?!\NAre you stupid or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, Iceberg is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ribbit!\N--Hm? What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so what, you don't want\Nhelp from the likes of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! Can you keep up with my ship design?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you? Do you still have the\Nskills after doing demolition for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone from Tom's Workers is here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't have to build a ship\Nin a place like this, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it's a ship for the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something we can do to help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good if you rush through it all\Nby yourself and do a sloppy job, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... You guys don't have\Nto work on the backstreets?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The others said that since they\Ncouldn't come, at least we should go help,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if he was working on a\Nreplacement for that pirate ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice story...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand in my way, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We'll show you\Nthe skills of those at Dock #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky's building a ship for us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. You were sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then, he's a nice guy after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's a nice guy! Yep, he's a nice guy!\N--I'm looking forward to seeing the new ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's a nice guy!\N--Well then, why don't I go\Nout shopping while we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when will that ship be finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he came by yesterday,\Nhe said he needed five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, four more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a strange dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you call that a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the 100 million\NBerries we had in here go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that. I gave it to them to buy meat\Nand booze and stuff for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gave it to them? It was our money!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was our party, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We don't have much left!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can imagine! In the end,\Neveryone in town showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a real blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we got a good deal with the ship,\Nso there's no problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:22:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get gorgeous furniture for the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go hunt for a bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami! I'm gonna go out and have fun,\Nso give me some spending money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,@#$%&!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, why does water-water\Ncandy taste this good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.67,0:22:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I put it on top of cotton candy and eat it,\NI don't know what'll happen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--My... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:22:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Girl in Search of Her Yagara!\NGreat Search in the City of Water!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
